                name: 'Leg Extensions',
                category: 'legs',
                description: 'Leg extensions are an isolation exercise that specifically targets the quadriceps, making them an effective movement for developing definition and strength in the front of the thighs.',
                image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1593079831268-3381b0db4a77?q=80&w=1469&auto=format&fit=crop',
                muscles: ['Quadriceps', 'Rectus Femoris'],
                steps: [
                    'Sit on a leg extension machine with your back against the backrest.',
                    'Hook your feet under the padded bar, adjusting it to rest on your lower shins.',
                    'Grasp the handles on the sides of the seat for stability.',
